      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve adjustment and a thorough inspection of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the precise turn-in and mechanical grip these chassis are renowned for. While showing honest signs of use, the powertrain remains robust, delivering linear acceleration up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
